column5: Nope, thats 16 Mile..... thats a small pier, now that its been in the paper, add another 20 guys to it lol.... Burt
While I'm not in the picture I live about 5 minutes away and fish there regularly. Way more numbers at bronte. 16 mile just takes a better picture.
OMG Rob... call them and tell them to blur their background next time....
The background isn't the issue for that photo. It's the foreground....and the caption on a national newspaper's web site.
